{"tid":1651193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求？狗賊死全家？咪傻啦","createTime":"2019-10-13T09:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T09:20:25.000Z","uid":217098,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"194f3ff87261149320eea3cdc4d3007ea89cbabb","tid":1651193,"uid":217098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:16:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span></strong></span><br />\n呢條先係我地唯一既出路<br />\n我地再點抗爭令林鄭下台<br />\n法案唔再推<br />\n班狗賊點比人清<br />\n都只不過係短時間既好轉<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中共</span></strong></span><br />\n先係一切禍害既起點<br />\n我地必須獨立<br />\n先可以令我地仲有未來<br />\n即使推倒重來又如果<br />\n呢家搵到錢個班仆街係點搵架？<br />\n一係親共，一係就壓榨人民<br />\n咁樣既社會結構係你想要既咩？<br />\n屌你老母，幾撚多人死，幾撚多人被自殺<br />\n仲要掛住中國係香港前面？<br />\n我地比人內陸殖民緊喳"},{"pid":"64dde3b6e314bfef9183913af645c23bad00e3c2","tid":1651193,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:17:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c8fc29490ac233546da1c6c21d4b437c4ca7f56","tid":1651193,"uid":217098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:17:46.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"c1bac0d11c9899ed7aecd552ee8a62410d02e5fc","tid":1651193,"uid":217098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:18:28.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"6d2226c4fdfacbac3ccba7e4f12268fb9dd0052b","tid":1651193,"uid":217098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:18:42.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"2f31837c890e659ee4f229bf7ec92eac37bfbdf8","tid":1651193,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:18:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4c11433395e4fa4d110415c14f46881ae57526a","tid":1651193,"uid":217098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:18:55.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"6831cfd742e859c75f3ab0697ec294375ea9a1ad","tid":1651193,"uid":217098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score